  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to access the tolerability of INS37217 Intravitreal Injection
      when administered intravitreally in subjects with macula-on or macula-off rhegmatogenous
      retinal detachment (RRD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
